      <div class="row mt-3">
        <h3 class="text-center fw-bold">Mission Statement</h3>
        <p2 class="text-center"
          >Reconizing that career development is a life long process, the
          mission of Career Development & Counseling Center (CDCC) is to guide
          and support students as they explore and further understand
          themselves,<br />
          evalute career options, gain valuable experience, develop
          post-graduation career plans, and achieve their full potentials.</p2
        >
      </div>
      <div class="row mt-3">
        <h3 class="text-center fw-bold">Long Term Goals</h3>
        <p class="text-justify">
          <li>
            Build a strong collaboration among SDA institutuins by creation
            goals and activities that are mutually beneficial to instiutions.
          </li>
          <li>
            Provide information that enchanced student's interest and abilities
            through career exploration.
          </li>
          <li>
            Provide guidance and support through internship and employment
            opportunities for students and alumni.
          </li>
          <li>
            Provide updated and useful information related to scholarshops,
            volunteer work or community services, etc.
          </li>
          <li>Establish network by seeking MoU and agreements.</li>
          <li>Establish alumni network and build strong collaboration.</li>
        </p>
      </div>
